  <entry>
    <title>中国区 AWS EKS ARM64/AMD64 混搭Node</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2021/02/10/eks-mult-architect/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2021/02/10/eks-mult-architect/</id>
    <published>2021-02-10T08:15:52.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-02-10T09:13:34.876Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://aws.amazon.com/cn/blogs/china/how-to-easily-deploy-hybrid-architecture-nodes-on-eks/">reference</a></p><ol><li>创建集群：</li></ol><p><code>eksctl create cluster --name eks-multi-arch --without-nodegroup --region=$&#123;AWS_REGION&#125;</code></p><ol start="2"><li>创建AMD64 node group</li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">eksctl create nodegroup \</span><br><span class="line">--cluster eks-multi-arch \</span><br><span class="line">--region cn-northwest-1 \</span><br><span class="line">--name x86-mng \</span><br><span class="line">--node-type m5.large \</span><br><span class="line">--nodes 1 \</span><br><span class="line">--nodes-min 1 \</span><br><span class="line">--nodes-max 3 \</span><br><span class="line">--managed</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li>创建ARM64 node group</li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ eksctl create nodegroup \</span><br><span class="line">--cluster eks-multi-arch \</span><br><span class="line">--region cn-northwest-1 \</span><br><span class="line">--name graviton-mng \</span><br><span class="line">--node-type m6g.large \</span><br><span class="line">--nodes 1 \</span><br><span class="line">--nodes-min 1 \</span><br><span class="line">--nodes-max 3 \</span><br><span class="line">--managed</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="4"><li>创建结果<br><img src="https://webnote.s3.cn-northwest-1.amazonaws.com.cn/20210210-arm64nodegroup.png" alt="arm64&amp;amd64nodegroup"></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://aws.amazon.com/cn/blogs/china/how-to-easily-deploy-hybrid-architecture-nodes-on-eks/&quot;&gt;reference&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;创建集群：&lt;/</summary>
      
    
    
    
